<div class="container">
<div class= "col-lg-12">
<div class="card my-5 rounded-0">
  <div class="card-body">
    <h2 class="card-title text-center">Contact Us</h2>
  </div>
</div>
   <div class="my-5">
<p class="lead">
We would love to hear from you! Whether you have a question about our <strong>web development courses</strong>, want to discuss a project with us, or simply want to connect with us, feel free to reach out.
</p>

<p class="lead">
Please fill out the form below, and we’ll get back to you as soon as possible.
</p>
<div class="my-3">
<%= form_with model: @contactform, url: contactform_path, method: :post, local: true do |form| %>

        <div class="row">               
           <div class="col-lg-6">
               <div class="form-group">
                   <%= form.label :user_name,class:"mb-2" %>
                   <%= form.text_field :user_name , class:"form-control rounded-0 form-control-lg"%>
               </div>
           </div>
           <div class="col-lg-6">
               <div class="form-group">
                   <%= form.label :user_email ,class:"mb-2" %>
                   <%= form.email_field :user_email , class:"form-control rounded-0 form-control-lg"%>
               </div>
           </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
           <div class="col-lg-12">
               <div class="form-group">
                   <%= form.label :user_message , class:"mb-2" %>
                   <%= form.text_field :user_message, class:"form-control rounded-0 form-control-lg"%>
               </div>
           </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
        <%= form.submit "send message" , class:"btn btn-warning my-3 rounded-0"%>
       <%= link_to 'Back To Contact Us', contactform_path ,class: "btn btn-outline-warning my-3 rounded-0"%>
            </div>
        </div>
<% end %>
</div>

<h3>Other Ways to Reach Us</h3>

<p class="lead">
    If you’d prefer to contact us directly, you can also reach us at:
</p>

<ul class="lead">
<li><strong>Email</strong>: support@infinitidev.com</li>
<li><strong>Phone</strong>: +123-456-7890</li>
</ul>

<p class="lead">
Follow us on social media to stay updated with our latest courses and projects:
</p>

<ul class="lead">
<li><strong>Twitter</strong>: <a href="https://twitter.com/infinitidev">@infinitidev</a></li>
<li><strong>LinkedIn</strong>: <a href="https://linkedin.com/company/infinitidev">Infinitidev</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>